_______________________________________________________________________________
"Repulsion Field"   
        Through the use of this power, the psionicist can create
        a telekinetic forcefield behind which he can stand, completely
        separated from other people and events in the area.  The
        psionicist will be able to look and talk in the room, but cannot
        pick anything up, attack, or be attacked.  Any items or conversation
        WITHIN the forcefield can be completely separated from those
        outside.
 
SP Cost:  50		Guild Level:  10	Potential Points:  4
 
Command:  rfield  |  killfield  (To kill a field you have created)
